name: [V2.0]Artist: 青十紅(Aobeni) | 青十紅 artist's painting style
description:
青十紅 Style LoRA V2

简体中文 | English

仿青十紅的作画风格的LoRA模型。

权重建议值：0.8 (or 0.5~1)

基于模型：CreationMixV1 Trimmed

训练信息：共计296张原画，迭代592步。

其他的一些建议：EasyNegative。此外，万一畸形四肢换个种子重画就行。

The LoRA model mimics Aobeni's painting style.

Recommended weight value: 0.8 (or 0.5~1)

Based on model: CreationMixV1 Trimmed

Training information: A total of 296 paintings (including cropped images) with 592 iterations.
Other recommendations: EasyNegative. Moreover, in case of distorted limbs, try starting over with a different seed.

--

如果你创作出了好作品，欢迎分享它。如果它无法满足你的需求，我是说，我的朋友，请不要给出一星好评。千里马常有，而伯乐不常有。

If you've created something good, feel free to share it. If it doesn't meet your needs, I mean, my friend, please don't give a one-star 'praise'. Fine horses are often found, but good horsemen are rare.
